<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /></view><text>风险学员详情</text></view>
  <scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content">
    <view class="profile-card"><image src="{{avatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view><view><text>{{student.name}}　{{student.gender}}</text><text>{{student.risk}}</text></view><text>{{student.classInfo}}</text><text>到期日：<text>{{student.expiry}}</text>（还剩{{student.remainingDays}}）</text></view><view><text>{{student.remaining}}</text><text>课时</text><text>剩余课时</text></view></view>
    <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">⚠ 风险原因与依据</view><view class="risk-table"><view><text>风险原因</text><text>{{student.reason}}</text></view><view><text>依据数据</text><text>{{student.evidence}}</text></view></view></view>
    <view class="chart-grid"><view><text>▣ 上课与课消趋势（近8周）</text><view class="bars"><view style="height:72rpx;"></view><view style="height:48rpx;"></view><view style="height:48rpx;"></view><view style="height:36rpx;"></view><view style="height:24rpx;"></view></view></view><view><text>◷ 课消率趋势（近8周）</text><view class="risk-line"><view></view><text>50%　25%　50%　25%</text></view></view></view>
    <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">☵ 家长互动摘要（近30天）</view><view class="interaction-grid"><view><text>3</text><text>发起沟通</text></view><view><text>1</text><text>家长回复</text></view><view><text>20%</text><text>回复率</text></view><view><text>平均18h</text><text>平均回复时长</text></view></view><text class="last-message">最近沟通内容：询问课后表现，提醒剩余课时及到期时间，推荐续费优惠活动。</text></view>
    <view class="section-card owner-card"><view class="section-title">♙ 负责人</view><image src="{{coachAvatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><text>{{student.owner}} · <text>负责人</text></text><button>☎</button><button>☵</button></view>
    <view class="split-grid"><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">建议跟进方案</view><text>1. 了解学员上课体验与困难</text><text>2. 强调课程效果，展示学员进步</text><text>3. 提醒课时到期，推荐续费方案</text><text>4. 提供专属优惠，促成续费</text></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">跟进时间线</view><view class="timeline-row" wx:for="{{timeline}}" wx:key="time"><view></view><text>{{item.time}}　{{item.text}}</text><text>{{item.status}}</text></view></view></view>
    <view class="section-card task-link"><view><text>关联续费任务</text><text>{{student.name}} · 续费跟进任务　剩余{{student.remaining}}课时｜{{student.expiry}}到期</text></view><text>任务状态　<text>进行中</text></text><button bindtap="openTask">去处理</button></view><button class="primary-button" bindtap="newFollowup">新建跟进记录</button><view class="safe-space"></view>
  </view></scroll-view>
</view>
